{
  "stem": "7744.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when they liquidated the ghetto, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and the children were left behind, I was left behind, too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember in the middle of the night-- and I'm quite sure that my uncle must have given half of Krakow away for that-- people came looking for me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I heard people yelling and calling my name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was taken to Plaszow in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I believe that I also know that there were some fires in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My husband says to me, the ghetto did not burn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I am saying that there were fires in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I, I wish sometimes-- you know, I've been so busy with my life, making a, making a new life for myself, that I haven't, maybe, dwelled enough on it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In fact, it's only in the last couple of years that I've been talking about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My husband has been talking to the children about it since they were little.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I never said anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, and it's been difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's, it's difficult to recall, especially when you've tried to forget.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in Plaszow, I was mostly hidden-- and again, on the bunks, hidden behind whatever in darkened part of, of, of the camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And life was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember horrible hunger in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I remember horrible fear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But the hunger started much later, and the sickness, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I don't remember hunger in Plaszow for myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother, again, was, was a needed entity, because they needed her knowledge in, in, in the languages.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
